 target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"92f097e726df629516f6117167cb539e2b1589f8","tid":1913351,"uid":230104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:08:59.000Z","msg":"謝偉俊同何君堯呢四年數錢數都手軟，多謝御用界票師<br />\n<br />\n中間超人威脅不大"},{"pid":"3dabbc7517af5cc240a8a43d30ad4e19b8080b28","tid":1913351,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:11:25.000Z","msg":"上屆就係無宣誓，唔夠堅定，先有一批on99亂鳩咁投，毫無策略，無大局觀，以為投心儀既就可以贏"},{"pid":"e9e89a2c19f8e52edbf474d04c306704f00850c3","tid":1913351,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:13:11.000Z","msg":"不服來辯"},{"pid":"63776eee1e0825ddd77bb4bd212d5bead9f12d4b","tid":1913351,"uid":4917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:14:44.000Z","msg":"屌你老味柒達"},{"pid":"292b128f52dd620e838727d95803b16b06201e2f","tid":1913351,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:16:05.000Z","msg":"一定要投本土 冇本土投素人<br />\n如果唔係點會見到港共政府瘋狂DQ<br />\n香港人覺得一個梁天琦坐監都唔夠<br />\n要十幾廿個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db420ec9d63e6adbbb5295d19509ec8b1fe1d915","tid":1913351,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:16:16.000Z","msg":"又𠝹票論<br />\n即係今年邊個唔初選又係鬼？"},{"pid":"5df419673ee95414c04231baf65d6f305b2c8495","tid":1913351,"uid":200895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:31:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rvz35Tj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frvz35Tj.jpg&h=db14c194&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60dc29b329a8d71076ea6f4b3a6d779ec9301f65","tid":1913351,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote"